  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is the safety and efficacy of Buprenorphine/Naloxone in the
      treatment of opioid dependence. A compassionate use study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to provide follow-up compassionate use treatment and evaluate
      long term safety and efficacy of a buprenorphine/naloxone combination tablet for opiate
      dependence treatment for subjects who have completed Cooperative Study 1008 A and B.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
